    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a baking tray (or two!) with <strong>baking paper</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> sweet potato rounds </strong>and<strong> onion wedges </strong>to the baking tray[s] with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for an initial 10 min or until everything's slightly softened</p>",
      "order": 3,
