    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and<strong> half</strong> your<strong> balsamic sun-dried tomato paste </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Season with a crack of <strong>black pepper</strong> and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> – this is your <strong>sun-dried tomato & balsamic dressing</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
