    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p><p>Once the quinoa is cooked, remove the pot from the heat and stir through the <strong>remaining sun-dried tomato paste </strong>and<strong> chopped garlic </strong>– this is your <strong>sun-dried tomato & balsamic quinoa</strong></p>",
