      "instruction": "<p>Once the sweet potato and onion have had an initial 10 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven and push the veg to one side</p><p>Add the <strong>sun-dried tomato & balsamic quinoa</strong> to the other side and spread it out evenly</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 15 min or until the veg is completely tender and the quinoa is crunchy – this is your <strong>roasted veg & crunchy quinoa</strong></p>",
